%% Control One Provisioning Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as Operator UI
    participant UI as Web UI (React)
    participant API as Control Plane API
    participant Queue as Worker Queue
    participant Worker as Worker Executor
    participant Provider as Cloud/Hypervisor Provider
    participant Agent as Node Agent

    Operator->>UI: Select provisioning template
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/jobs {type: provisioning, tenant_id, payload}
    API-->>UI: 202 Accepted + Job ID
    API->>Queue: Enqueue provisioning job
    activate Queue
    Queue->>Worker: Deliver job for execution
    deactivate Queue
    activate Worker
    Worker->>API: Update job status = running
    Worker->>Provider: Call provider adapter with template payload
    Provider-->>Worker: Provisioning result / artifacts
    Worker->>API: Update job status = succeeded/failed + event log
    deactivate Worker
    API->>Agent: Notify via hooks / polling (optional)
    API-->>UI: Job status stream (poll/WebSocket)
